data.description: Welcome to your future home in Gloucester, VA – where everyday comfort meets affordability! It's the perfect blend of cozy and practical. Step inside, and you'll find a layout that just makes sense. The living space is relaxed and inviting, with a brand-new HVAC system (2021) and a wood wood-burning fireplace, creating a chill vibe that feels just right. The kitchen is down-to-earth and ready for action. Cook up your favorite meals in a space that's both functional and easygoing with a central kitchen island and plenty of storage space. With three bedrooms, everyone gets their own slice of privacy, making it a home that works for the whole crew.  Oh, and only 5 mins from Gloucester Courthouse and 22 mins from Coleman Bridge! This isn't just a house; it's a down-to-earth, everyday kind of home. If you're looking for a comfy spot in Gloucester that won't break the bank, this one's calling your name. Your new home sweet home awaits!
